    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>DEMO CONTENT -&gt;</u></strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Step into the fractured world of <i>Forgotten Fragments</i>!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>This demo offers a glimpse into both solo and co-op play with 10 handcrafted levels per mode, secret stages to uncover (3 in solo, 4 in co-op), and hidden collectibles waiting to be found. Whether you're exploring alone or with a friend, there’s plenty of mystery to piece together.</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>FULL GAME CONTENT -&gt;</u></strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The Spheres Are the Key</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the spheres power to light the torches and complete the level. But it won't always be easy: you'll need to aim your throws well and launch them before the time limit runs out...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1498080/extras/6bfd91c45267f921833e6465346282ed.poster.avif?t=1758045851\" width=612 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1498080/extras/6bfd91c45267f921833e6465346282ed.webm?t=1758045851\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1498080/extras/6bfd91c45267f921833e6465346282ed.mp4?t=1758045851\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Two Campaigns, Two stories</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uncover Enid's story as you recover the forgotten fragments, or team up with a friend to unravel all the secrets of the two-player campaign. Each campaign has its own levels!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1498080/extras/3cc4dd3015aabc0f433f70d252aa8f01.poster.avif?t=1758045851\" width=638 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1498080/extras/3cc4dd3015aabc0f433f70d252aa8f01.webm?t=1758045851\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1498080/extras/3cc4dd3015aabc0f433f70d252aa8f01.mp4?t=1758045851\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Over 120 Levels to Conquer</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each campaign features 4 worlds to explore, with over 60 levels each. But the challenge doesn't end there, as you can replay each level to improve your time and become the best!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1498080/extras/7eb049d83656010b7f2b5d994a50ac18.poster.avif?t=1758045851\" width=764 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1498080/extras/7eb049d83656010b7f2b5d994a50ac18.webm?t=1758045851\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1498080/extras/7eb049d83656010b7f2b5d994a50ac18.mp4?t=1758045851\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Epic Boss Fights!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At the end of each world, you'll face a powerful boss, each with their own unique mechanics. Get ready to apply everything you've learned during your adventure to emerge victorious in these battles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1498080/extras/aef3d5cac656b0b66636c549e29dc44a.poster.avif?t=1758045851\" width=638 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1498080/extras/aef3d5cac656b0b66636c549e29dc44a.webm?t=1758045851\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1498080/extras/aef3d5cac656b0b66636c549e29dc44a.mp4?t=1758045851\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Find the hidden collectibles and the secret levels!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find the hidden collectibles in some levels to unlock skins and customize your characters. Make sure to explore every corner: to play the secret levels, you'll need to light special torches...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1498080/extras/c759075eb8013d59888733390e5e6d57.poster.avif?t=1758045851\" width=460 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1498080/extras/c759075eb8013d59888733390e5e6d57.webm?t=1758045851\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1498080/extras/c759075eb8013d59888733390e5e6d57.mp4?t=1758045851\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1498080/extras/3aeb9b7e492bf8bf9f31d59d6545f63d.poster.avif?t=1758045851\" width=460 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1498080/extras/3aeb9b7e492bf8bf9f31d59d6545f63d.webm?t=1758045851\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1498080/extras/3aeb9b7e492bf8bf9f31d59d6545f63d.mp4?t=1758045851\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1498080/extras/f179b426c475802529b9f62425fcdf02.poster.avif?t=1758045851\" width=460 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1498080/extras/f179b426c475802529b9f62425fcdf02.webm?t=1758045851\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1498080/extras/f179b426c475802529b9f62425fcdf02.mp4?t=1758045851\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
